\n\r\nIn the end, I think what I learned would allow me to backpatch rgx with the updates, but I'm honestly pretty happy with the smaller footprint of this dependency and its goals, so probably will just maintain easygpu moving forward. I toyed with inlining it and easygpu-lyon, but I opted to keep those crates more focused. Frankly, I've been tempted to split Kludgine into a few crates.", "created_at": "2020-10-09T16:18:03Z", "updated_at": "2020-11-09T03:23:16Z", "closed_at": "2020-10-09T16:44:46Z", "merged_at": "2020-10-09T16:44:45Z", "merge_commit_sha": "77090b1c195572d916679b326f7257a7304f9f7f", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/khonsulabs/kludgine/pulls/35/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/khonsulabs/kludgine/pulls/35/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/khonsulabs/kludgine/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/khonsulabs/kludgine/issues/35/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/khonsulabs/kludgine/statuses/7eca8dec40ce4bf71b77a49e29516f2ef29fe933", "head": {"label": "khonsulabs:updateWgpu", "ref": "updateWgpu", "sha": "7eca8dec40ce4bf71b77a49e29516f2ef29fe933", "user": {"login": "khonsulabs", "id": 50191483, "node_id": "MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjUwMTkxNDgz", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/50191483?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/khonsulabs", "html_url": "https://github.com/khonsulabs", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/khonsulabs/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/khonsulabs/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/khonsulabs/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/khonsulabs/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/khonsulabs/subscriptions", "